i never really showed any signs as a kid, besides the fact that i liked things to be straight. it developed late last year, around december. i never really noticed it because it was very mild and didn't affect me much at all. but as soon as school shut down because of COVID-19, my OCD got BAD. i have no reasonable idea for why my OCD got so severe so fast simply because of school closing
F.Y.I. i am 15 years old, turning 16 in a little over 2 months
